# TLS certificates go here (generated by generate-certs.sh)
# See infra/.gitignore — *.pem, *.crt, *.key are excluded from git
#
# Run this to generate certs:
#   bash infra/gateway/certs/generate-certs.sh
#
# Generated files:
#   ca.key           — Root CA private key (4096-bit RSA)
#   ca.crt           — Root CA certificate (self-signed)
#   server.key       — Server private key (2048-bit RSA)
#   server.crt       — Server certificate (signed by CA, SAN: localhost, *.nt219.local)
#
# Week 3+: Replace with Vault PKI Engine auto-issued certs
